column2: Add OpenJ9 support to Windows Launchers.

column3: This is a proposed fix for https://youtrack.jetbrains.com/issue/IDEA-202981 and makes the Windows launcher comptatible with OpenJ9. The only changes are path checks for the OpenJ9 jvm.dll locations.
However, I tested it by manually copying the .exe generated by the sln, so some help to understand how the executables are generated for each version of IntelliJ would be appreciated.
Add Openj9 j9vm paths and checks
